snippet.title: Wargroove: Double Trouble - DLC Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Team up and lead the Outlaw faction to strategic victory, with new criminal Commanders in the new free DLC, Wargroove: Double Trouble! 

Coming to PC, Nintendo Switch and Xbox One on February 6th. Coming to PS4 soon!

Steam: http://bit.ly/DoubleTroubleSteam
Nintendo eShop: https://bit.ly/2FNE2hh
Xbox Store: https://bit.ly/2RYy2IK
PlayStation Store (EU): http://bit.ly/WargroovePS4EU
PlayStation Store (US): http://bit.ly/WargroovePS4US
Humble: https://bit.ly/2MLtAHx

Visit the Wargroove website & take our Faction Quiz: wargroove.com
For more information and to keep up to date with the latest development news, keep an eye on our dev blog : wargroove.com/blog

Facebook: facebook.com/wargroove
Twitter: twitter.com/wargroovegame
Reddit: reddit.com/r/wargroove
Discord: https://discord.gg/2Kwh6fP
